
Help for bing-bar-parser.pl v2012-11-10

Perl script to parse selected fields from a given Bing Bar searchhs.dat file

Usage: bing-bar-parser.pl [-h|help] [-file filename]
-h|help ... Help (print this information). Does not run anything else.
-f file ... Bing Bar searchhs.dat file to be parsed.
-d ........ Applies URI decoding to search terms (eg replaces %20 with space).

Example: bing-bar-parser.pl -f /cases/searchhs.dat -d
